'''博馬高原'''（'''Boma Plateau'''）位於[[蘇丹|蘇丹]]東南部[[瓊萊省|瓊萊省]]和[[東赤道省|東赤道省]]，與埃塞俄比亞高地連接，是區內雀鳥的重要濕地。[[過度放牧|過度放牧]]和利用槍枝過度捕獵在威脅著野生生物。<ref name=birdlife>{{cite web|url=http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/sites/index.html?action=SitHTMDetails.asp&sid=6814&m=0|title=Important Bird Area factsheet: Boma, Sudan|date=2009|work=BirdLife IBA Factsheets|publisher=Birdlife International|accessdate=19 January 2010|archive-date=2009-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090103042616/http://www.birdlife.org/datazone/sites/index.html?action=SitHTMDetails.asp&sid=6814&m=0|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1977年，博馬國家公園成立，面積228萬公頃。<ref name=birdlife/>博馬高原是全球數個有野生[[小果咖啡|小果咖啡]]生長的地方。<ref>{{cite book|author=Charrier A, Berthaud J|title=Coffee: Botany, Biochemistry and Production of Beans and Beverage|editor=Clifford MH, Wilson KC|publisher=AVI Publishing|location=Westport, Connecticut|date=1985|page=20|chapter=Botanical Classification of Coffee|isbn=0-7099-0787-7}}</ref>

